                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <p>How well does it follow the principles of effective visualization?</p>
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <p>What works well about this visualization?</p>
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <p>How could it be improved?</p>
                  </li>
                </ul>
