                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <p>Does your communication respect the communities or populations represented in your data?</p>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </statement>
            </task>
            <task>
              <statement>
                <p>
                  Based on your review, make at least three specific improvements to your communication materials to make them more ethical and effective.
                </p>
              </statement>
            </task>
